Jason is writing a program to check if a number is even, but it is giving him an error. Below is Jason’s code:
```cpp
#include 
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int number = 4;  // Number to check

    // Error in condition
    if (number % 2 = 0) {
        cout << "Even" << endl;
    } else {
        cout << "Odd" << endl;
    }

    return 0;
}
```

**Expected Output:**
```default
Even
```

